summary: This is an FBI 302 form documenting a proffer interview conducted on December 20, 2019, at the United States Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York. The interview was attended by federal prosecutors and law enforcement agents, and the document contains information provided by an individual under a proffer agreement related to the investigation.

keyFacts: A proffer interview was conducted on December 20, 2019, as part of the investigation.
The interview took place at the United States Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York.
Attendees included Assistant United States Attorneys, an FBI Special Agent, and an Office of Inspector General Special Agent.
The document references attached notes taken by an AUSA on September 9, 2019.
The document is an FBI 302 form, which is an official record of an interview, and contains neither recommendations nor conclusions of the FBI.
